article_title: Four-Vehicle Wreck On I-244 Slows Traffic Into Downtown Tulsa - NewsOn6.com - Tulsa, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports - KOTV.com
article_text:
A four-vehicle collision on Interstate 244 at Southwest Boulevard showed northbound traffic Tuesday morning.

The crash reduced traffic to one lane until crews could clean it up.

There were no reports of anyone being injured in the crash.
